arts.ttl: St. Pauli safety all but confirmed as Eintracht Frankfurt left waiting on top four
arts.sum: St. Pauli left Deutsche Bank Park believing they are as good as safe from the drop after holding hosts Eintracht Frankfurt to a draw that leaves the Eagles fretting over UEFA Champions League qualification going into the final weekend. Michy Batshuayi fires home Eintracht Frankfurt's equaliser.

arts.sum: The race for the final two Champions League spots will go down until the final matchday after Eintracht Frankfurt drew against St. Pauli.

arts.ttl: Eintracht Frankfurt vs. St. Pauli preview: Die Adler seeking UCL qualification
arts.sum: Eintracht Frankfurt will have the chance to secure Champions League qualification when they face St. Pauli on Sunday.
